VABL – Open Tournament

VABL – Open Tournament

Hooray!

September 1

Open Tournament Boxing Event at Melbourne Pavilion

Experience the thrill of competitive boxing at the Melbourne Pavilion’s Open Tournament Boxing Event! Fighters from various backgrounds and skill levels will step into the ring, showcasing their dedication, technique, and heart. Join us for an action-packed day filled with intense bouts, sportsmanship, and community spirit. Don’t miss out on this exciting opportunity to support local talent and witness the passion of boxing at its finest!
